{"tid":1625020,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"五大訴求 缺一不可 光復香港 時代革命 去左邊？","createTime":"2019-10-05T05:37:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T07:53:30.000Z","uid":162061,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a7d2232d383f5ba7f303909470477f6435b42f06","tid":1625020,"uid":162061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:37:13.000Z","msg":"唔該所有手足 冷靜d <br />\n依家唔係同你割蓆<br />\n但唔該你地唔好因為一時憤怒 乜都唔記得哂<br />\n記唔記得當初由撒回惡法 你地叫和理飛唔好割？<br />\n點解依家有人話要臨政 又港獨<br />\n口講就話和理飛大多數 但你地有無理到後面手足既感受？佢地係咪認同呢個理念？<br />\n<br />\n花左4個月時間 文宣花左幾大努力話比全世界聽<br />\nFive demands not one less <br />\n<br />\n竟然比一條蒙面法搞到你地無哂理智<br />\n於是就有人宣讀要臨政/臨時議會/什至港獨<br />\n咁樣比哂理由港共班含家產話你地搞港獨<br />\n<br />\n我知大家都好嬲 好無助 <br />\n我亦都理解你地咁做既原因<br />\n但我仍然相信呢條路係要靠堅持 <br />\n要一步一步行番黎<br />\n<br />\n所以我唔該大家 將重點同槍口對番準<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 港共政權"},{"pid":"cfdacf3cd61567220862f82071f402989383e50e","tid":1625020,"uid":162061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:41:25.000Z","msg":"重點"},{"pid":"6f81f78b55d7da1f85e55bbf1bed853ee9d37a2e","tid":1625020,"uid":162061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:42:31.000Z","msg":"認清目標"},{"pid":"d4206a116d05d74e6e5e7d7909aab61fff249a3d","tid":1625020,"uid":162061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:45:28.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a5715cb61051621960e1489bd67db121af76fa01","tid":1625020,"uid":278295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:48:22.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c6adcb7a254b10bdd1714f27e089681a27bdc9a1","tid":1625020,"uid":162061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:57:26.000Z","msg":"Push!"},{"pid":"ab617f0988399a9662324fac4a3a83ffeabe093f","tid":1625020,"uid":162061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:46:22.000Z","msg":"Push ar"},{"pid":"e3bed868f3929adadeda468c48e4bb0c84d24bf4","tid":1625020,"uid":162061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl